  "rationale": "<p>Factor: 3x \u2212 15 = 3(x \u2212 5). The numerator is (10x \u2212 7)(x \u2212 5). Since x &gt; 5, x \u2212 5 \u2260 0 and can be cancelled: (10x \u2212 7)(x \u2212 5) / (3(x \u2212 5)) = (10x \u2212 7)/3. Choice (a) is correct.</p>",
